org.bluedb.api.keys

Class LongKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bluedb.api.keys.ValueKey
      • org.bluedb.api.keys.LongKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BlueKey>, BlueKey

    public final class LongKey
extends ValueKey
    A key that can be mapped to a value in a BlueCollection or BlueIndex. Values inserted with this key will be ordered and will fill up an entire segment before creating a new one. I-node usage will grow as new segments are needed.
